    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it looks and feels just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve kept it tucked away in the garage and pampered it like crazy, so it\u2019s still in that gorgeous, spotless condition you\u2019re looking for. It drives like a total dream\u2014smooth, quiet, and super responsive. If you want a ride that feels brand new without that dealership headache, come say hi and take it for a spin. You\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an uncompromising 997.1 Carrera S, an analog benchmark featuring the 3.8L M97 flat-six engine. This naturally aspirated powerplant utilizes Variocam Plus valve timing and a dry-sump lubrication system, delivering linear torque through a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) for variable damping and four-piston monobloc aluminum calipers for exceptional thermal management during high-performance deceleration. The factory-original Arctic Silver Metallic paint is free of swirls or road rash, while the undercarriage remains remarkably clean with no signs of heat cycling or fluid seepage. This specimen represents a collector-grade investment with all original VIN tags intact and a comprehensive service history.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
